%===============================================================================
% File Name     : <pst-icon-sports-olympic-2024-tools.sty>
% Description   : LaTeX package for postscript Olympic 2024 icons using PSTricks
% Documentation : pst-icon-sports-olympic-2024.tex
% This package contains sporting elements and tools.
% A depiction of the action: Each pictogram features a distinctive tool of the sport it represents—such as arrows for archery, bicycles for cycling, or rackets for tennis.
% A depiction of the playing field: There can be no sporting performance without a playing field; the pictograms therefore showcase a distinctive aspect of the pitch or track used for each sport.
% The axis of symmetry: Lastly, all of the pictograms are designed around an axis of symmetry to reinforce their “coat of arms”-like aspect.
% https://olympics.com/en/paris-2024/the-games/the-brand/pictograms
